WEBVTT

05:01.550 --> 05:02.750 line:80%
That's all we've got.

05:03.430 --> 05:04.360 line:80%
Please spare us.

05:04.800 --> 05:05.630 line:80%
Get lost.

05:06.720 --> 05:08.360 line:80%
If you dare come back
and cause trouble again,

05:08.360 --> 05:11.090 line:80%
you'll deserve it
even if you get beaten to death!
